{"title":"FOX XL Mudguard extends protection for your latest 36 & 38 mountain bike fork","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/10/12/fox-xl-mudguard-extends-protection-for-your-latest-36-38-mountain-bike-fork/","date":1634022076000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085320/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_wet-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"FOX XL Mudguard extends protection for 36 38 MTB forks, wet\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085320/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_wet-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085320/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_wet-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085320/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_wet-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085320/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_wet-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085320/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_wet-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085320/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_wet.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-274445\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Better protection is here for the latest FOX 36 &amp; 38 forks thanks to the new XL Mudguard. Extending the seal &amp; stanchion protection of their standard short mudguard, the new XL offers 85% more coverage for those who ride in wetter, muddier condition, still with the same clean no-zip-tie setup.</p><h2>FOX XL Mudguard extends protection for MY21+ 36 &amp; 38 MTB forks</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085316/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085316/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_side.jpg\" alt=\"FOX XL Mudguard extends protection for 36 38 MTB forks, side profile\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085316/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_side.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085316/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_side-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085316/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_side-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085316/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_side-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085316/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_side-768x461.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>There are plenty of simple, low-cost &amp; effective strap-on fork fender solutions to keep dirt &amp; mud off of your fork’s seals and often also out of your eyes. But it’s hard to beat the clean-looking, well-executed setup of the fender made by the fork manufacture, just for your fork. Now, this new FOX XL Mudguard delivers a perfectly integrated, extended fender for model year 2021 &amp; newer <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/04/07/fox-38-enduro-fork-now-in-our-midst-plus-2021-fox-36-and-dual-crown-fox-40/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FOX 36 &amp; 38</a> trail, all-mountain &amp; enduro mountain bike forks.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled.jpg\" alt=\"FOX XL Mudguard extends protection for 36 38 MTB forks, angled\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085312/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_angled-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>A good mudguard will help your seals last long and keep your fork sliding smoother between regular service intervals. And now this one increases coverage up front, extends it out back, and adds material around the fork arch for increased seal &amp; stanchion protection.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085309/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_riding-dirty.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085309/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_riding-dirty.jpg\" alt=\"FOX XL Mudguard extends protection for 36 38 MTB forks, riding dirty\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085309/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_riding-dirty.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085309/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_riding-dirty-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085309/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_riding-dirty-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085309/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_riding-dirty-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/12085309/FOX-XL-Mudguard-extends-protection-for-36-38-MTB-forks_riding-dirty-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>With the same clean 2-bolt mounting with clips around the bleed ports for extra support like the original short mudguard, the new XL keeps max tire clearances of 29×2.5″ or 27.5×2.7″. The new FOX XL Mudguard for the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/04/07/fox-38-enduro-fork-now-in-our-midst-plus-2021-fox-36-and-dual-crown-fox-40/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">36 &amp; 38</a>&nbsp; sells for $25, just like the XL for the 40 DH fork.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.ridefox.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>RideFOX.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e17d23c03d441f038a45f12678246c49f62971dfa83ab2faff41ccc28e4f8b1b","category":"Cycling"}